se.lypson.common.collections
Interface IListIterator

All Superinterfaces:
IForwardIterator
public interface IListIterator
extends IForwardIterator

An iterator for lists that allows the programmer to traverse the list in forward or backward direction. The list can be modified during traversion, either by this class or the underlying list class.

Author:
Tobias Persson
